        public static void exportStatsAsHtml(SparkTrainingStats sparkTrainingStats,
                                     java.lang.String path,
                                     org.apache.spark.SparkContext sc)
                              throws java.lang.Exception
        Generate and export a HTML representation (including charts, etc) of the Spark training statistics
        Note: exporting is done via Spark, so the path here can be a local file, HDFS, etc.
        Parameters:
        sparkTrainingStats - Stats to generate HTML page for
        path - Path to export. May be local or HDFS
        sc - Spark context
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - IO errors or error generating HTML file

      • exportStatsAsHtml

                                     long maxTimelineSizeMs,
                                     java.lang.String path,
                                     org.apache.spark.SparkContext sc)
                              throws java.lang.Exception
        Generate and export a HTML representation (including charts, etc) of the Spark training statistics
        Note: exporting is done via Spark, so the path here can be a local file, HDFS, etc.
        Parameters:
        sparkTrainingStats - Stats to generate HTML page for
        path - Path to export. May be local or HDFS
        maxTimelineSizeMs - maximum amount of activity to show in a single timeline plot (multiple plots will be used if training exceeds this amount of time)
        sc - Spark context
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - IO errors or error generating HTML file
